author: @Minavis_Penguin
text:
I don't know why none of the comments are not talking about the lyrics that RosÃ© constructed. The lyrics of this song is telling that you really want to fully love that person but you have a doubt that you're not able to fulfill it and chose to reject his affection and confession meant to be given for you either before or after the commitment because you don't want him to have high expectations from you that you two will last but instead, this song portrays that you should tell him in an early pace that you're not able to give it all as he might end up hurting himself.

All of us want to love and to be loved by someone but sometimes, we're unsure of it if we could give them the enjoyment from us so it's better to think of it and cut that bound between you two rather hurting someone at the other end from expecting your love to them and this song wrote and sang by RosÃ© is a perfect example.
